dct_title_s: States in the Big Ten Academic Alliance
dct_description_sm: This dataset contains the boundaries of the 11 states in the Big Ten Academic Alliance as of 2022. It was derived from the cartographic boundary files available on https://www.census.gov/geographies/mapping-files/time-series/geo/carto-boundary-file.html.  Data are generalized representations of geographic boundaries at 1:500,000.
